WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy B1-M03: School, study and work. Learners practise summarise information through classroom language, learning habits, jobs, workplace communication. The teacher models will/going to/present continuous for future, introduces vocabulary such as subjects, study skills, jobs, duties, workplace phrases, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
